## Brand Guidelines

### Color Palette (Miró + Dark)
```css
:root {
  /* Backgrounds */
  --bg-primary: #0B0F19;      /* Deep charcoal */
  --bg-surface: #111827;      /* Card/section background */
  
  /* Text */
  --text-primary: #E5E7EB;    /* Main text */
  --text-muted: #9CA3AF;      /* Secondary text */
  
  /* Miró Accents (use sparingly) */
  --miro-red: #FF3B30;
  --miro-blue: #0A84FF;
  --miro-yellow: #FFD60A;
  --miro-green: #30D158;
  
  /* Functional */
  --accent: #0A84FF;          /* Links, primary CTAs (Miró blue) */
  --success: #30D158;         /* Positive actions */
  --warning: #FFD60A;         /* Alerts */
}
```

### Typography
- **Name (hero):** Bold sans-serif, large (clamp 2.5rem to 4rem)
- **Headings:** Clean sans-serif, medium weight
- **Body:** Serif or mono, 1rem, line-height 1.6
- **Spacing:** Generous whitespace (1.5-2rem between sections)

### Visual Rules
- **No gradients** (flat colors only)
- **Minimal shadows** (use subtle border/glow instead)
- **High contrast** (readability > aesthetics)
- **Animations:** Subtle, purposeful (no bounce/spin)
- **Icons:** Simple SVG or Unicode emoji

