## Common Tasks

### Adding a new section
1. Add HTML structure with semantic tags
2. Style with existing CSS variables
3. Ensure mobile responsiveness
4. Test accessibility (keyboard, contrast)

### Adding an animation
1. Use CSS `@keyframes` for loops
2. Use `transition` for interactions
3. Add `prefers-reduced-motion` check
4. Keep duration < 0.5s for interactions

### Adding a new page
1. Copy structure from existing page
2. Update `<title>` and meta tags
3. Link from navigation
4. Test all links work

