## Troubleshooting

### Animations not working
- Check `prefers-reduced-motion` settings
- Ensure element has `transition` or `animation` property
- Verify keyframes are defined

### Layout breaking on mobile
- Check `max-width` on containers
- Use `clamp()` for fluid typography
- Test in DevTools responsive mode

### Colors not matching design
- Verify CSS variables are defined in `:root`
- Check for inline styles overriding
- Use DevTools color picker to inspect

